task.summary: Initial Commit All the files as well as branches.

Initial Commit
All the files as well as branches. Fixed the Sender.py.

Frame Packet Handlers in Sender
Frame the packet handlers to handle the responses of the Receiver when a message is sent back to the Sender (almost always a simple ack that must be checked to validate which packets to send).

Format the messages and setup the file loading framework
Set up the framework for the file loading function. This is to be the testing form of it and the initializer for the sequence number.

Get the Sender and Receiver Talking
The Sender and Receiver are talking. The seqno of the Receiver is only incrementing by one, which seems to contradict the specifications laid down by the professor for the Sender? Looking into this.
